title.rendered: 65W GaN Ultra Fast Triple Port Wall Charger

excerpt.rendered:
BAYKRON Premium 65W GaN Ultra Fast Triple Port Wall Charger with USB-A 18W and USB-C PD 65W & USB-C PD 20W, for Standard UK wall outlets

  • FEATURES – GaN devices have a high reliability, and can ensure the charger for a long stable output. It can achieve stable output power and low energy operation. The surface temperature rise of the power adapter will be controlled within 30-35º.
  • POWERFUL – GaN chargers typically produce 10 degrees less heat than regular chargers. GaN devices have ultra-high power conversion efficiency, more than 10% more than regular chargers.
  •  MULTIPLE DEVICES – 65W multi-port GaN charger can charge laptops, tablets and other large electronic products, supporting a variety of protocols. up to three devices at a time. Exceeds the high demand charging of mobile phones, portable power supplies, headphones and other devices allowing ALL to be charged at the same time.
  • ULTRA COMPACT – The GaN technology greatly reduced volume, is an integrated fast charging category.  Whether it is daily use at home or travel, it is the ultimate experience brought by fast charging, saves time, thus reducing the cost of waiting time.
  • OVER VOLTAGE PROTECTION – Multi-way safety protection: over voltage protection, over current protection, electrostatic protection, short circuit protection, temperature protection.
  • COMPATIBLE – Input of 110V – 240V (U.S. & World Standard) designed for UK standard wall outlets.
  • 65W COMPATIBLE FAST CHARGING PROTOCAL DEVICES:Apple2.4A, Samsung 5V2A, DCP, QC2.0, QC3.0, AFC, FCP, SCP, PD3.0, PPS.
  • 65W COMPATIBLE DEVICES: Notebooks: Macbook, Huawei, Xiaomi, & Samsung. Smartphones: iPhone 8-14, iPad Pro, iPad Air 5, iPad 6 (PD fast charging) iPhone 4-7 (normal charging) Samsung S6-S22 Huawei P9-P50 Huawei Mate9-Mate50 Qualcomm phones: Xiaomi 6-12 Redmi K50 LG G8 Sony Xperia 5 Google Pixel 5 VIVO and OPPO: Normal charging.
  • WARRANTY – 2 Year international warranty with proof of purchase on all BAYKRON products
